{"tid":1549944,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"明居正：中共十一在香港的死線在9月10日~15日","createTime":"2019-09-07T13:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:18:42.000Z","uid":286206,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6f0ec02889e8d71f92af943aa5c942be3cca7305","tid":1549944,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-O6Sxs1UTMw&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR3dCzjhQ95fQy0VqubgwxZMR8Muea29ReipjRXBEVQgrAgrL_YnDn8fGCA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-O6Sxs1UTMw%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26fbclid%3DIwAR3dCzjhQ95fQy0VqubgwxZMR8Muea29ReipjRXBEVQgrAgrL_YnDn8fGCA&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=0838bf2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-O6Sxs1UTMw&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR3dCzjhQ95fQy0VqubgwxZMR8Muea29ReipjRXBEVQgrAgrL_YnDn8fGCA</a><br />\n<br />\n不嬲佢D分析都唔差，不過好似呢度比較少人討論(?)。<br />\n明居正雖然係台灣退休教授，但對中共派系研究好有權威佢背後仲有成隊Team幫佢手套料同分析而且跟香港既事跟我好貼。絕對唔係燒山之流。<br />\n我都覺得Make Sense，我知我唔會叫得暫停大家上街。總之呢幾日自己留意下納粹軍隊同政府舉動小心D無壞。"},{"pid":"a3bc5d1956fe16949119ff6383596d2c29de593d","tid":1549944,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:32:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1Frbvn52bdc&amp;fbclid=IwAR3gj1R6nd9N4DrovtqYECszkpqBlr0wjTkkfWHxXJHatYWNpudTL9M13Ow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1Frbvn52bdc%26fbclid%3DIwAR3gj1R6nd9N4DrovtqYECszkpqBlr0wjTkkfWHxXJHatYWNpudTL9M13Ow&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=abfbbac0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1Frbvn52bdc&amp;fbclid=IwAR3gj1R6nd9N4DrovtqYECszkpqBlr0wjTkkfWHxXJHatYWNpudTL9M13Ow</a><br />\n<br />\n有時間可以睇埋呢段。"},{"pid":"1295d9bb9bb2d9b82f9d2cfd94a7ecd262e476ba","tid":1549944,"uid":19728,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:33:11.000Z","msg":"最新個評論係話會拖到十月一號國殤日後處理"},{"pid":"60aae0de589bf156b84be6039d565c37ba76b6d4","tid":1549944,"uid":272292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a88c6570018e4a8a20f4cbf81798c93a29afdd2e","tid":1549944,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:38:18.000Z","msg":"之前有d巴打講過佢，我都有留意下。<br />\n佢兩三個星期前就勸林鄭要走人黎自保，今日體返覺得都準。<br />\n不過佢似乎比較少提美國立法對港府可以造成的影響。"},{"pid":"da1217f1631b26f630977cdb90b6ca6b454d0235","tid":1549944,"uid":277899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>美國新聞聽日 一 定 影 我 地</strong></span></span>，所以<br />\n<br />\n聽日<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定要和理優！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>不塗鴉、不雷射、不闖入</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定一定要 莊 重！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有人搞事都要冷靜理性解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家而家求緊美國呀 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>態度行為要上得大枱</strong></span></span>呀！"},{"pid":"9d65253aa52f3f6e9ffbca9fffd1cdc85fe529cd","tid":1549944,"uid":286206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"60aae0de589bf156b84be6039d565c37ba76b6d4","tid":1549944,"uid":272292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"cit